Title: WWE Day 1
Actors: Brock Lesnar, Ettore Ewen, Bobby Lashley
Plot: The inaugural WWE Day 1 Premium Live Event. Big E puts the WWE Title on the line against Brock Lesnar, Seth Rollins, Kevin Owens and Bobby Lashley in a Fatal 5-Way Match. Becky Lynch defends the Raw Women's Title against Liv Morgan.
